name: The Walkthrough Acoustic Sessions
description:
This is the debut acoustic EP from Will Parry!

	The tracks are:

	Nine
What Went Wrong
Mary, Alone
Hello Chloe

	Expect harmonies and intricate guitars as heard online but recorded professionally!

	The cost includes postage and packaging to mainland UK only.
If you live somewhere else and want the EP then drop us a message at:

	willparrymusic@hotmail.co.uk

	We will be more than happy to sort something out for you :]
